    "project_desc": "The project aims to provide an accurate knowledge of the historical significance and doctrinal impact of the Ilahiyyat (Metaphysics) of Ibn Sina (Avicenna)’s Kitab al-Shifa' (Book of the Cure, or: of the Healing) – one of the masterpieces of Medieval Arabic philosophy in the Islamic world, and one of the most influential and widespread works of falsafa of all times – by means of a reconstruction of the manuscript tradition, a reliable edition, an English translation, and a doctrinal explanation of the text of the work.",
